  <brief_title>Effect of Ready to Use Therapeutic Food (RUTF) Supplement After an Episode of Malaria Falciparum on Weight</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effectiveness of Ready to Use Therapeutic Food (RUTF) in Catch up Growth in Children After an Episode of P. Falciparum Malaria</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Medecins Sans Frontieres, Netherlands</agency>
